It doesn't appear to be occurring for all tabs, but in most of my open tabs when I type a 'j' into the location bar and then delete it with the backspace character, it is deleted, but an artifact remains. The artifact looks like a tiny period. It appears as though almost all of the 'j' is erased, with the tiny tip of the bottom left remaining.

Reproducible: Didn't try
